\>To avoid a repeat of that incident, it is necessary to thoroughly
eliminate the Rista Church and its clergy from the territory.

\>With the help of the collaborators of the Gospel Agency, the
influence of the Rista Church in this territory has certainly
declined in recent years.

\>Therefore, the incident with the nun should have been insignificant.
\>Monitoring her movements through the contract mark was even useful
as entertainment for the collaborators.

\>It has been confirmed that she is undoubtedly a nun without any
backing, but unbelievably she repaid all her debts and terminated the
contract. \>

\>On the contrary, the atmosphere of faith in the Rista Church is
gradually returning to the entire city. \>Although she is completely
different from Luminea in both personality and appearance, we have
reached a consensus that this woman is dangerous for us.

\>We need to act immediately. \>As a suitable candidate, there is a
searcher who will take on any dirty work.

\>The effectiveness of the black pattern may weaken or not be
inherited due to mixed blood. \>Especially in recent years, the
effectiveness has significantly decreased.

\>Young orphans who have nothing and live in the shadows of the
streets are just right. \>Like the former king, they are made to give
up their vitality in exchange for protection. \>

\>It is dangerous for anyone other than collaborators to know about
the black pattern in Lestania. \>Make sure to always manipulate the
information that it is just a disease.

These children seem to be orphans from the shady alleys. Moreover, all
of them are suffering from Black Scrawl...

What on earth is going on? What are they doing with Black Scrawl
patients...?

Anyway, we will take responsibility for protecting these children
here. Please do not worry.
Haah, haah... Adults... every single one of them is trash...

I was brought here... and instead of food, I was made to do some
strange contract...
And then, my body is tired... It feels somewhat painful...
I hate it, but... I don't want to go back to the shady street...

\>A valuable book that contains records of the magic used by the king
in the past. \>To be precise, it is a written record of what ...
taught the king.

\>Among them is necromancy using a contract spell with the dead. \>The
summoned dead are different from naturally occurring evil spirits and
obey the commands of the practitioner.

\>By using evil spirits, continuous psychological and physical damage
can be inflicted on the target. \>Currently, there are very few in
Megista who can deal with evil spirits, \>which can also lead to a
decrease in the loyalty of lords and the followers of the Rista
religion.

\>Target citizens, especially craftsmen, as a priority. \>If craftsmen
disappear, the weakening of the Megistus region will progress rapidly.
. If I had slept, there would have been many guards. *yawn*...

It's not like I'm hurting her or anything. I'm also a former orphan,
you know. I'm just a caretaker. I don't know anything.

However... one thing I can say is that before coming here, the
children were not afflicted with the Black Death.
